  "title": "💎 Retail Sales Associate (Jewellery) | Multiple Outlets | Basic from $1,800 + Comm + VB",
  "description": "<p><strong>Multiple Outlets | Basic from $1,800 + Commission + VB</strong></p>\n<p>📍 <strong>Locations:</strong> Yishun / Jurong West / Tampines<br>\n💰 <strong>Salary:</strong> Basic $1,800 + Commission (Average up to $3,500) + Allowances<br>\n🕒 <strong>6 Days Work Week | Retail Hours | Immediate Hiring</strong></p>\n<h3>🛍 <strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist with daily store opening and closing duties</li>\n  <li>Attend to customers and convert enquiries into sales</li>\n  <li>Maintain store cleanliness and ensure displays are neat and attractive</li>\n  <li>Stay positive, energetic, and motivated to hit sales targets</li>\n  <li>Support daily store operations and teamwork</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>🔍 <strong>Job Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>No experience required — training provided</li>\n  <li>Must be motivated, friendly, and willing to learn</li>\n  <li>Able to communicate in English &amp; Mandarin<br>\n <em>(Malay-speaking is an advantage to liaise with diverse customers)</em></li>\n  <li>Basic computer knowledge</li>\n  <li>Service-oriented with good communication skills</li>\n  <li>Able to work retail hours, weekends &amp; public holidays</li>\n  <li>6 days work week</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>📅 <strong>Working Hours</strong></h3>\n<p>⏰ <strong>9:30 AM – 7:30 PM</strong><br>\n📌 <strong>Off Day:</strong> As scheduled by management<br>\n📌 <strong>Outlet Rotation:</strong> Required</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 23C1703 </p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R1762582 </p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Choo Sian, Jabez</p>",
